{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM02_150.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x16,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey Plachta, can I ask you a question?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You used to be an alchemist, right? I don't really understand this, but... What exactly is alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... There are actually several types of alchemy, so it's difficult to generalize..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "The alchemy you use, and that which I used in the past, is a \"technique to fulfill the wishes of materials.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "The wishes... Of materials?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes. This technique listens to the materials' desires, then turns those materials into what they wish to be."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "That is the alchemy we use."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "H-huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "For example, let's say there is a plant that wishes \"to heal people\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Alchemists must first realize that wish. Then, borrowing some power from nature, we give that power to the plant."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "In that way, we help the plant turn into medicine with the power of healing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "In other words, alchemists are simply helping to fulfill the wishes of the materials."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...Sophie? You've been very quiet, did you understand all of that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry, Plachta. I was listening to all of it, but I didn't understand at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's okay. To tell the truth, you're actually subconsciously doing exactly what I explained."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Really!? But I've never heard the wishes of materials or anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure that's the case. It's not something that you can hear with your ears."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Although it seems some extremely skilled alchemists are able to hear the wishes of materials directly..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Regardless, while alchemy does require some concrete theories to function, one's senses are particularly important."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "You must cherish and hone your senses, to the point where you believe you can hear them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I got it. Thank you, Plachta."
        }
    ]
}